text: Lâm Anh Quang (born 24 April 1991) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as a defender for V-League (Vietnam) club Nam Định. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:V.League 1 players Category:SHB Da Nang F.C. players Category:People from Nam Định Province
